code: /**  * Creates a program target description from deployment classes.  *  * @param clusterId cluster id  * @param jobId job id  * @param <C> cluster id type  * @return program target descriptor  */ public static <C> ProgramTargetDescriptor of(C clusterId, JobID jobId, String webInterfaceUrl) {     String clusterIdString.     try {         // check if cluster id has a toString method         clusterId.getClass().getDeclaredMethod("toString").         clusterIdString = clusterId.toString().     } catch (NoSuchMethodException e) {         clusterIdString = clusterId.getClass().getSimpleName().     }     return new ProgramTargetDescriptor(clusterIdString, jobId.toString(), webInterfaceUrl). }
